    <div class="comment__content">
      
            <div class="text-content field field--name-comment-body field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item comment__text-content"><p>Hi. I live here in Georgia. Southwest corner. I was told plant carrots in the winter months. I got seed pods trays that can start the seeds. I was wondering if I can transplant the plants in the ground in February?  We have hot temperature in May in the 90's. Trying to the best time. Also like  to plant onions too. Both of them are cold weather plants for here .</p>
</div>
      <ul class="links inline comment__links">
